Once upon a time, there lived a monkey on a berry tree, which was on the banks of a river.
In the forest there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day when the crocodile was hanging out in the river,
he saw the monkey on the tree. The monkey generously offered him some berries. The crocodile ate the berries and the both became good friends. After getting home the
crocodile told his wife about the monkey. The cruel wife of mr croc was very eager to eat the monkey inspite of the monkey being her husband's friend...